name: TIGER KITCHEN
address: 5279 Still Creek Ave, Burnaby, BC V5C 5V1, Canada

hasMenuItem.name: Mega Classic Kimbap
hasMenuItem.description:
Gluten friendly.
Smoked chicken breast, Fish cake, Cheddar cheese. Rice, Roast seaweed, Pickled radish, Burdock root, Spinach, Carrot, and Sesame oil.

All gluten-free ingredients, though our kitchen isn't certified.
Heating it in the microwave for 30 seconds makes it much more delicious.
